In re Resignation of Barragate.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Barragate (1992), 64 Ohio St.3d 1201.]

(No. 92-919 Submitted May 19, 1992 Decided May 21, 1992.)

The resignation of Phillip A. Barragate as an attorney, Registration No. 0008575, is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
